#################################################################################################################
#  Platform control related macro definitions                                                                   #                                                  #
#     QOSA_LINUX_PLATFORM_FUNC         Primarily used in Linux systems                                          #
#     OSA_RDA8910_PLATFORM_FUNC        Primarily used for selection during 8910 project adaptation.             #
#     OSA_RDA8910_R06_PLATFORM_FUNC    8910 R06 has special characteristics as an application replacement.      #
#     OSA_QCX216_PLATFORM_FUNC         The QCX216 platform also provides application replacement                #
#     OSA_QCX217_PLATFORM_FUNC         The QCX217 platform also provides application replacement                #
#     OSA_ASR1903_PLATFORM_FUNC        The ASR1903 platform also provides application replacement               #
#     OSA_EIGEN718_PLATFORM_FUNC       The EIGEN718 platform also provides application replacement              #
#                                                                                                               #
#################################################################################################################

